                ranges are more versatile in terms of placement. Both types can
                experience issues such as malfunctioning burners, broken oven
                doors, and faulty control panels. Professional service
                technicians can diagnose and fix these issues, often involving
                part replacements and adjustments. Repair costs for both
                slide-in and freestanding ranges typically range from <b
                  >$150 to $400</b
                >. Regular maintenance and timely repairs can ensure that these
                ranges operate efficiently and have a long service life.
              </p>
